<div id="descriptionContainer">
  
      <div id="description" class="readable stacked" style="right:0">
        
<span id="freeTextContainer15247498600948739738">Peter Carey&apos;s Booker Prize winning novel imagines Australia&apos;s youth, before its dynamic passions became dangerous habits. It is also a startling and unusual love story. <br/><br/>Oscar is a young English clergyman who has broken with his past and developed a disturbing talent for gambling. A country girl of singular ambition, Lucinda moves to Sydney, driven by dreams of self-relianc</span>
  <span id="freeText15247498600948739738" style="display:none">Peter Carey's Booker Prize winning novel imagines Australia's youth, before its dynamic passions became dangerous habits. It is also a startling and unusual love story. <br /><br />Oscar is a young English clergyman who has broken with his past and developed a disturbing talent for gambling. A country girl of singular ambition, Lucinda moves to Sydney, driven by dreams of self-reliance and the building of an industrial Utopia. Together this unlikely pair create and are created by the spectacle of mid-nineteenth century Australia. <br /><br />Peter Carey's visionary brilliance, and his capacity to delight and surprise, propel this story to its stunning conclusion.</span>
  <a data-text-id="15247498600948739738" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

