<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/110417504-josh-wulfekotte"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_100x100-259587f1619f5253426a4fa6fb508831.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/110417504-josh-wulfekotte">Josh Wulfekotte</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Oscar was more or less raped by Miriam. He took this to be his fault for compromising her and immediately married her at the local courthouse. Lucinda<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Oscar was more or less raped by Miriam. He took this to be his fault for compromising her and immediately married her at the local courthouse. Lucinda had legally formalized their bet, and because Oscar had delivered the church on time the courts ruled he owned Lucinda's inheritance. When he died Miriam took control of all of Lucinda's assets, including the church which was meant to be a gift for Dennis Hasset. Because Dennis had rejected Miriam previously she spitefully re-gifted the church to another congregation. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
</div>
