              <span id="reviewTextContainer703445415" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer29660663523762311">Life is a game of chance. <i>Oscar and Lucinda</i> is a perfect stylization to <b>Charles Dickens</b> and at that the novel remains postmodern. In the end evil is punished and somehow good is punished too.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


